DEATH BY TREE!

Ludum Dare 25 Entry by Edii Knorand!

You are an evil tree which kills adventurers. You can summon evil bunnies and causes a global damage.

Controls:
A + Left Click: Summons Bunny
S + Left Click: Causes Harm
Q: Quit


To Compile:
  $ make

To Run:
  $ cd dbt/
  $ ./ld25-dbt

Thank you and have fun!

Dependencies: SDL, SDL_image.

Get SDL from your package manager or http://www.libsdl.org/
Get SDL_image from your package manager or http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/
